description:
Arisugawa Kyoko, a self-proclaimed ordinary high school girl, fell down and died in a bathroom, then met a god called the Creator God and was reincarnated in a different world.

She is reborn in a completely unknown world, and begins her new life as Alice.

A new world and a new life.

All kinds of encounters, adventures and dramas are waiting for her.

Yes, this is a story about reincarnation in a different world that can be found anywhere.

The main character is a girl who doesn’t know any of this kind of templates, priviledges, flags, conventions, cheats, common sense, etc… Except that she’s a girl who doesn’t know any of that stuff.

A forest that explodes and blows up when you scream.

Her reincarnated race is the true ancestors of vampires that became extinct 30,000 years ago.

The first dragon she encountered was the Black Death Ruin Dragon.

A number of statuses that would astound even a god.

「Elves? Race? I don’t quite understand, maybe it’s like the Pekingese race? It doesn’t matter what.」

「What? I am Vampire?」

「Immortality…? Huh? Then where’s the talk about the nice body that make people envy?」

「Eighty billion in magic power… that’s definitely a lot. No, it might not be too much.」

This is a story about Alice, an ordinary girl who knows nothing about such otherworldly things.>
